    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/f60ce7b5219ed836397adf348a387688.avif?t=1739125679\" width=615 height=87 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单就是最好</h2>在我们全新的多人在线游戏中，体验前所未有的令人肾上腺素飙升的坦克大战。&quot;League of Felt Tanks&quot;是一款充满乐趣的经典坦克游戏。坦克射出的子弹会在墙壁上反弹，躲避敌人的子弹，尽全力射击！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/a3e0d22f82fb3649fd77929c7ec366fb.avif?t=1739125679\" width=320 height=84 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在线多人游戏</h2>1~3 人 COOP 模式 &amp; 2~8 人 PVP 模式<br>召集你的朋友一起玩！您可以单独玩，也可以与陌生人一起玩！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长的快乐</h2>拾取道具可增强坦克性能。<br>让我们用强化后的坦克击败对手吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/2a6865953a0b6f36521c2333237403e4.poster.avif?t=1739125679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/2a6865953a0b6f36521c2333237403e4.webm?t=1739125679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/2a6865953a0b6f36521c2333237403e4.mp4?t=1739125679\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >坦克定制</h2>来吧 是时候打扮一下了。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/432be31de5bb73e38453c40687104ae5.poster.avif?t=1739125679\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/432be31de5bb73e38453c40687104ae5.webm?t=1739125679\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1713310/extras/432be31de5bb73e38453c4